title: The Good News Gospel Train - A Gospel Collection
description:
The Good News Gospel Train - A Gospel Collection (2007)

This is a collection I put together for myself and several friends based on many months of research. Clocking in at a little over 2 hours of the best gospel music I could find, it&#039;s a compilation that&#039;s meant to be both entertaining and educational - if you listen to all the songs and read the extensive liner notes that are included (written by myself, also), you should get a pretty good introduction to gospel music as a whole. 

I put a hell of a lot of research into this thing (and money buying CDs and time listening to MP3s) that I didn&#039;t want to go to waste, so I&#039;m providing this to the wider world so that other people can benefit from my efforts. Enjoy!
